description:
Protect your Osprey Poco child carrier on planes, trains and buses with this convenient carry case.

  • Made of lightweight yet durable 210-denier nylon
  • Removable shoulder strap for comfortable carrying through airports and bus terminals
  • Lockable zippers let you use your own TSA approved lock
  • Insert your business card in the ID window to help the carrier find it's way home again if it gets lost in transit
  • Dimensions are 78x37x34cm. Total volume is 94L
  • Fits Osprey Pogo and Pogo Plus child carriers
name: Osprey Poco Carrying Case
